<div class="infra-preview-panel description-panel"><p>TEST leads in the enhancement of sensor performance for an effective early warning system for landslides (EWS-L). TEST manages sensor data from the tilt and soil moisture sensor. By performing experimentations, TEST ensures the quality of the sensor data readings to prevent false alerts. </p><br>
<p>SWAT provides Website automation tools for easier access to the technology developed by the project. The goal of SWAT is to carry out faster dissemination of early warning information for an effective early warning system for landslides (EWS-L).</p></div>